 Dajaxice (djity branch)
 -----------------------

	install our dajaxice from github

>git clone git@github.com:youen/django-dajaxice.git dajaxice
>cd dajaxice
>[sudo] python setup.py install




##############################
# Usual developper commands: #
##############################

Reset all applications:
	yes yes | ./manage.py reset revtext wiki portal project partner simplepage portlet blog moatserver style

Create new portal (all applications should be reset first):
	./manage.py create_portal

